'''劣地国家公园'''（{{lang|en|Badlands National Park}}）是[[美国|美国]]的一座[[美国国家公园列表|国家公园]]，位于[[南达科他州|南达科他州]]西南部，面积为{{convert|244000|acre|sqkm}}<ref name="VisitGuide">{{cite web | title=2008 Badlands Visitor Guide | work=Badlands National Park | url=http://www.nps.gov/badl/upload/BADL%20Planner%202008.pdf | format=PDF | accessdate=2008-05-17 | publisher=美国国家公园管理局 | archive-date=2008-05-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080516055001/http://www.nps.gov/badl/upload/BADL%20Planner%202008.pdf }}</ref>，有很多土丘、尖峰和草地。

其中劣地野生动物保护区面积为{{convert|64144|acre|sqkm}}，<ref name="VisitGuide"/>是美国[[濒危物种|濒危物种]][[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]][[黑足鼬|黑足鼬]]的生长地。<ref>{{cite web| title=Critical Park Issues - Reintroduction of the Black-Footed Ferret| work=Badlands National Park| url=http://www.nps.gov/badl/exp/issues.htm#bff| accessdate=September 26, 2005| archive-date=2006-08-19| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060819154342/http://www.nps.gov/badl/exp/issues.htm#bff}}</ref>

